{"tid":1569575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關唱歌，真係唔好淨係唱國歌啦！仲要做其他實事呀！！","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:38:28.000Z","uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7424a369830dbf88f3eafe17ab8a45144f311f65","tid":1569575,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"我知唱國歌振奮士氣、但是除左唱國歌、試問誰人未發聲同今天我<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係要諗清楚唱歌既「Purpose」</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要得到外國支持，一定唔可以淨唱上面既歌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">起碼一定要識唱英文版國歌同試問誰人未發聲</span></span><br />\n另外就是每次叫口號渣咪既人兄一定要讀一段「我地既訴求未獲政府回應，一定要堅持我地既訴求，要求外國介入」既英文段落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為外媒係完全唔知你班契弟唱歌做乜鳩（可能仲以為大家勝左開心大合唱添）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在場我見過有外國人黎「睇熱鬧」但完全唔識D歌又唔識口號<br />\n總之<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要講多D英文咁先有機會推上外媒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家場運動係必定要靠外國勢力，所以有D人會提議唱美國國歌<br />\n其實都是一個方法，但要強調唱美國國歌的原因是因為呢個是民主自由的象徵<br />\n但總之唔可以齋唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n同埋認真，可以唔使唱咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求、缺一不可"},{"pid":"09f37f920d24b4e1081611f68ac7b5bfea8dd2ef","tid":1569575,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}